<P>
Thanks to NBC, I can now get some work done because I won't have to sit in 
front of the TV watching my favorite game show. NBC took off the wonderful 
"Sale of the Century." When they cancel "Classic Concentration," I will sell my 
TV and go work for McDonald's. 
</P>
<P>
Virginia Charman, North Hollywood 
</P>
