<HEADLINE>
<P>
TAXES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The great thing about democracy is that we pretty much deserve what we get. 
Ronald Reagan and his string-pullers didn't make any secret about the fact that 
they believed in lower taxes for the rich. Now is not the time for those of us 
in the middle who have to make up the shortfall to scream and rend our 
clothing. After all, we are the very ones who put him there -- not once but 
twice -- and then elected his veep for yet another four years! 
</P>
<P>
Have no pity, George -- sock it to us. 
</P>
<P>
FRANK LAROCHE 
</P>
<P>
Ladera Heights 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA041689-0023 </DOCNO>
