<HEADLINE>
<P>
A GALLANT LADY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I recommend the Gallant Lady's cruise in the San Juan Islands. Read about it in 
your Travel Section last July (Travel Tips, July 24) and was there two weeks 
later. A welcome change of pace. Scenic, relaxing and excellent food. A true 
labor of love for Capt. Dick, his wife Lyn, family and crew. Nice people. A fun 
trip! For information, contact Gallant Lady Cruises, P.O. Box 1250, Vashon, 
Wash. 98070, or call (206) 463-2073. 
</P>
<P>
VIRGINIA McKINNEY 
</P>
<P>
Palm Springs 
</P>
</TEXT>
