<P>
Photo, Hands down -- San Diego shortstop Garry Templeton can't quite get to a 
bloop single hit by Atlanta's John Russell. Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
