90254, share an apartment in Hermosa Beach. TONY BARNARD / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Blue Blood Estates: Here's wealthy and famous Bel-Air with ZIP code 
90077 and expensive autos on empty streets. MARISSA ROTH; Photo, New 
