ago. Now he owns a sheep ranch near Bakersfield. ; Photo, Frank Iturriria, head 
of the Kern County Wool Growers Assn., was a shepherd when he immigrated to the 
U.S. 28 years ago. ROBERT GABRIEL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
