<P>
BACK TO SCHOOL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Guilford Dudley III ("Death Knell for Noblesse Oblige," April 2) may have had 
noblesse oblige instilled in him during his prep school years, but clearly 
spelling must have been a second-class subject; "Eaton," indeed. 
