<P>
Photo, Travis Williams passes out meal tickets to homeless people at a soup 
kitchen in Richmond, his hometown in the East Bay. ; Photo, Travis Williams, 
with memorabilia at his family's home in Richmnd (above), ANNE DOWIE / For The 
Times; Photo, returns a kickoff for the Green Bay Packers in '67 (right). 
Associated Press 
</P>
