the summer of 1985. ; Photo, "Soul Portrait" of herself was Megan Hart Jones' 
last work. It is on display at the Art Institute of Southern California. ; 
Photo, The artist described the spiritually-toned "Eternal Force" as her most 
ambitious drawing. ; Photo, Oil painting of clouds by Megan Hart Jones is on 
display at Art Institute of Southern California in Laguna Beach. 
</P>
