<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Due to an editing error, an incorrect figure was given in last week's Sunday 
Calendar for the typical share of ticket proceeds paid to leading pop 
attractions appearing at Irvine Meadows or the Pacific Amphitheatre. Such acts 
commonly receive 85% or more. 
</P>
